# Mandalorian Tower Defense

![Gameplay](gameplay.gif)

A 2D tower defense game built in **C++** using **SFML**, developed with **CLion** and **CMake**.

## Features

- Classic tower defense gameplay
- Multiple tower types (Archer, Fire, Bombardment, Barracks)
- Enemy waves with different enemy types
- Gold economy and tower placement system
- Music with smooth fade-in / fade-out
- Win / Game Over screens with star rating

## Controls

- `1` / `2` / `3` — Select level (Level 1 implemented)
- Left click on a blue 2x2 build tile — Open tower selection
- Left click on a tower icon — Build tower (if you have enough gold)
- Left click **Start Next Wave** — Trigger/queue next wave

## How to Run

1. Install **SFML 2.x**
   - macOS (Homebrew):
     ```bash
     brew install sfml@2
     brew link --force sfml@2
     ```

2. Open the project in **CLion**

3. Build and run the project from CLion

> All assets (images, audio, fonts) must remain in the project root directory.
